name: Penny Ziv
text: This place isn't even open. For good reason too. They were horrible. They brought the pizza hut name down. Constant turnover of employees and managers. Bad service. Messed up orders. So bad, I refused to go back or order from there more than a year before they closed. If I could they'd get zero stars

name: Chandler Zoltenko
text: Prior to closing permanently, the superior Pizza Hut was just as good as any other Pizza Hut there is, not having it limits restaurant choices in the area.

name: LaVina Cordelia
text: Alas, this Pizza Hut is no more.   Rumor has it that corporate offices effectively squeezed them out of business by demanding expensive renovations that this site could not justify by the amount of customers they received.  Quite a shame.

name: Mary Bowman
text: This Pizza Hut is closed! Since 12-31-2016 last time they open, business closed forever.
